fields.description:
Create AgentManager that holds all spawned agents.

## Deliverables
- src/agent/manager.ts

## Design (matching codex ThreadManager)
```typescript
class AgentManager {
  private agents: Map<AgentId, Agent>;
  private config: AgentConfig; // max_threads, max_depth

  spawn(options: SpawnOptions): Promise<AgentId>;
  get(id: AgentId): Agent | undefined;
  remove(id: AgentId): Agent | undefined;
  list(): AgentInfo[];

  // For AgentControl
  getState(): AgentManagerState;
}

interface AgentConfig {
  maxThreads: number;  // default 4
  maxDepth: number;    // default 3
}
```

## Acceptance Criteria
- [ ] Singleton instance per extension lifecycle
- [ ] agents Map stores Agent by AgentId
- [ ] spawn() creates agent, stores in map, returns ID
- [ ] spawn() enforces maxThreads limit
- [ ] spawn() tracks depth, enforces maxDepth
- [ ] get() returns agent or undefined
- [ ] remove() removes from map, releases thread slot
- [ ] list() returns all agents with id/type/status
- [ ] Config loaded from tau settings
